This is MAGRO (Most Advanced Gibbs Sampler by R Operation), a program
of Bayesian interface using R math library and usable by R environment.

The functionality of MAGRO is based on the BUGS program created by the
MRC Biostaticsitc Unit (http://www.mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk).

MAGRO is inspired by JAGS program created by Martyn Plummer 
(http://www-ice.iarc.fr/~martyn/software/jags/) and R project
(http://www.r-project.org)

